  <summary date="2024-03-27T19:43:28Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Stop Antiabortion Disinformation Act or the SAD Act 

This bill prohibits deceptive advertising for reproductive health services. Specifically, the bill makes deceptive advertising regarding whether a person provides contraceptives, abortion services, or access to licensed medical personnel subject to Federal Trade Commission enforcement.</summary>
